
USE URL https://reqres.in/
Test #1

1.Retrieve the list of users from the second page  using GET List Users request.
2.Make sure that the avatar's name contains id number.
3.Verify that the users' email addresses have the reqres.in domain.

Test #2

1.Register user POST request REGISTER - SUCCESSFUL
                             REGISTER - UNSUCCESSFUL

2. Create 2 test cases:
   - successful  registration
   -registration without password
3. Check error codes

Test #3
1. Verify that GET LIST<RESOURCE> returns data sorted by year.

Test #4.1
1.Try to delete the 2nd user and compare status code

Test #4.2
1. Update user's info and compare updated date with current date using PUT request.


